- und Distanzsprechen sowie deren Anwendung auf 15 Quellentexte vor.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aGerman languagexGrammar. 0aGerman languagexSemantics. 0aGerman languagexSyntax. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aCzicza, Dániel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFótos, Annamária, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGaál, Judit, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHegedüs, Ildikó, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHennig, Mathilde, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHennig, Mathilde, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHorváth, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKappel, Péter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMolnár, Petra, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMánássy, Ildikó, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRauzs, Orsolya, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZóka, Eszter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÁgel, Vilmos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÁgel, Vilmos, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2006z9783110276893oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978348464033740uhttps://do